Requirements
============

- ruby
- gems
  - sinatra
  - sequel
  - json
  - oca


The user has to provide a file named "one.rb":
CREDENTIALS   = "username:password"
ENDPOINT      = "http://localhost:2633/RPC2"
SCALARISIMAGE = "Scalaris4Contrail"
HADOOPIMAGE   = "Hadoop4Contrail"

It contains the url to the opennebula xmlrpc interface, the
usercredentials and the names of the scalaris/hadoop images.